title: All Stars voting link borken?
body: Whenever I try to click on the voting for all stars from the front page (oce.lolesports.com) it sends me here https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/all-star-voting-2018 and there is nothing on the site. Anyone else having this problem or know how to fix it?

replies.body: Worked fine for me, have you tried a different browser?
Ah, used Safari and that worked, thanks. Chrome wasn't working for some reason.
